1931;;Murder at Midnight;;American;;Frank R. Strayer;;Alice White, Aileen Pringle;;mystery;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Murder_at_Midnight_(1931_film);;A murder during a game of charades at a society party leads the police to begin the hunt through the guest-list for a motive and culprit, involving a changed will and booby-trapped telephones. The killer strikes several more times to conceal his or her identity, until all is revealed.